Praktikum_1

Class Rechteck

  • java.lang.Object
    • Praktikum_1.Rechteck
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable, Geometrie

    class Rechteck
extends java.lang.Object
implements Geometrie, java.lang.Comparable
    This class represents a Rechteck from just two points. We do not have any error checking here, like: min > max and trust the user (Hope this works).
    Author:
    Stephan Schauerte
